  "texts": [
    "Larkey [2] contributed to patent search and classification, aligning with CPC's goal of effective categorization.",
    "CPC research has spanned language barriers, precision, and deep learning to advance patent classification and analysis.",
    "Notably, Al-Shboul and Myaeng's work [5] introduced \"Wikipedia-based query phrase expansion\" to enhance CPC's search precision and recall.Due to the rapid advancements in deep learning, an increasing number of studies are being employed in the realm of CPC research.",
    "Prasad [6] employed Cooperative Patent Classification (CPC) to conduct a comprehensive search for bioremediation patents, contributing to an enhanced understanding of the patent landscape in this domain.",
    "Shalaby et al. [7] introduced an innovative method using Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) networks enhanced the accuracy of patent classification, offering greater adaptability to changing patent taxonomies and more efficient patent organization and retrieval."
  ],
